    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6682876/" class="title-link">说朴刀，有同篇作者，说大枪，不丰富，很难得。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6682876"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/50894789/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50894789-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/50894789/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">树竟无</span>
